text: Edward Tickell (9 February 1861 - 4 January 1942) was a British sports shooter. He competed in the men's 50 metre pistol event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1861 births Category:1942 deaths Category:British male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Great Britain Category:Shooters at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Cheltenham
